extends layout.pug
block content
  .jumbotron.jumbotron-fluid.jumbotron-singleCourse.text-center.bg-transparent
    .bg-primary-transparent.position-fixed.left.top.z-minus.h-100
      img.half-transparent.w-100.h-100.object-fit-cover(src='/media/bg1.jpg')
    .jumbotron-courses-container.text-white
      h1.display-1.mt-5.mb-3.text-white Company Tours
      p.lead.mb-3 Lets us visit your office.
  .container
    .bg-light
      .py-5
        .px-md-5.py-5    
          .px-md-5
            .px-md-5
              .px-lg-5.pb-lg-5.text-center
                h3.mb-5.text-muted We organize tours with our students on a regular basis. Every Wednesday we perform a trip through the digital-sector and visit some of the tech startups to give our students a feeling what it means to be  a developer. Are you or your company interested in hosting on of this events? Write us a message!
                h4 We offer company tours in the following locations: 
                  .mb-3
                  each location in locations
                    span.badge.badge-primary.mr-3.mb-3=location.name
              h2.text-center Get in touch!
              +contactform